Instructions -> Add to documentation later

Build and Push Wordpress container to the cloud.

Requirements:

Docker
Make
AWS CLI logged in
Jq

1. ECR Login

make login


2. Build

make build


3. Publish
make publish

4. deploy-wp - deploy upodated container image

make deploy-wp

5. plan terraform deploy with container tag

make plan

6. apply terraform

make apply

destroy terraform

make destroy

7. do everything in one go

make all
